 />\n<br />\n解放軍方面當住美軍會幫先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"同規模我估你係講緊武力上？<br />\n<br />\n當港共壟斷左係香港嘅武力正當使用，仲要無限量金錢資助警隊，點樣先可以有一個團體可以壓制到佢地？<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得硬碰硬唔會嬴到，眼見香港冇本錢武裝革命，我相信國際輿論／經濟制裁更加可取。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"國際輿論好似已經到左極限咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />暫時各國應付疫情疲於奔命<br />\n都冇辦法住"},{"pid":"8f3ff4849d54bc92fec3c8f7ca2514dbb1235f5f","tid":2016364,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:21:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d21bb985d903f083a776a15d6241ab4152e59a7","tid":2016364,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf117daf1fcb70b9c5de3d67419d64008fc27858","tid":2016364,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5865bc499b4aaee81bb3d7d68d32c7ad16b24a9c","tid":2016364,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240c52a918ab31ff0aa7b7b67d60849c7d0f7740","tid":2016364,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a3546c0011cad32a23cb032fdf502eb9b9470a","tid":2016364,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:09:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TgE4TN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TgE4TN&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=d052a18c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TgE4TN</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}